<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>nǐ shì dēng guāng 迦南160</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 nǐ shì dēng guāng jiù yào bǎ quán jiā zhào liàng,
 nǐ shì zhǒng zi jiù yào luò rù tǔ rǎng,
 nǐ shì huó shuǐ jiù yào bù tíng de liú tǎng,
 nǐ shì chén xīng jiù yào shǐ zǎo xíng de rén huān chàng,
 shén ràng wǒ men lái dào zhè gè shì jiè shàng,
 yào gěi rén dài lái hé píng yǔ xī wàng,
 róng yào zhǔ de míng, zhāng xiǎn shén de ài,
 chéng zào zài shān shàng shì bù néng yǐn cáng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>160</hymn_number>
</song>